<directions xmlns:php="http://php.net/xsl">&gt;
<step><![CDATA[slice the zucchini 3mm thick, then cut in strips lengthways and then across, to get 3mm dice]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[chop the onions]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[put salted water to boil ]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[melt the butter with oil, sautè the onions 5m on mid heat]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[add the zucchini and sautè ]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[meanwhile crush the aniseed and mint in pestle]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[cook the fusilli as per normal]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[in a food processor blend the black beans and stock. season with salt and pepper]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[add the mint + aniseed blend (6) to the zucchini (5), stir a bit]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[add the beans (8) to the zucchini (9)]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[when the pasta is ready stir into the sauce and serve]]></step>
&gt;</directions>
